Name
       timing_disable_lib_pulsewidth_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_lib_pulsewidth_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false (performs checks)

       When  set to true, disables timing model pulse width checks during tim-
       ing analysis.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

